Package: stokes
Type: Package
Title: The Exterior Calculus
Version: 1.2-4
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    Deriv,
    testthat,
    markdown,
    rmarkdown,
    quadform,
    magrittr,
    covr
